  <description><![CDATA[<p><span>Caringly run by our good friend Frau Weiss, the Hotel Eggerwirt is centrally located in <a data-udi="umb://document/4fb215d0c5bf48a09eae325fb09985f3" href="/{localLink:umb://document/4fb215d0c5bf48a09eae325fb09985f3}" title="Soll">Söll</a> and well loved for its high standards of service. </span></p>
<h2><span>A family favourite</span></h2>
<p><span>This family-run hotel has a comfortable lounge with open fireplace and is full of Tyrolean charm and character. Inghams guests return year after year for the warm welcome and relaxed atmosphere.</span></p>
<h2><span>Dining</span></h2>
<p>The hotel offers an extensive buffet breakfast everyday, with once weekly cooked option. You can enjoy a three course evening meal with choice of main dish plus salad buffet six days of the week. From 4th January 2025 there is no evening meals on Wednesdays. This gives you the chance to explore the local restaurants Söll has to offer.</p>
<h3>Exclusive to Inghams</h3>
<p>As a ski specialist tour operator we carefully select the very best accommodation in our resorts and package them with flights and transfers, so that you can make the most of your holiday. We have an exclusive agreement with Hotel Eggerwirt the only UK tour operator to package and sell holidays here - all the more reason to book with Inghams today!</p>]]></description>
